REMOVETRIGGER wind
ON wind DRAW 0 SWAPPOINTS X1 Y1 (X1 + 1) Y1

REMOVETRIGGER TestTrigger
ON TestTrigger DRAW ELEMENT:Earth FILLEDRECT 68 73 170 170
ON TestTrigger DRAW ELEMENT:Plant FILLEDCIRCLE 150 150 70 4000
ON TestTrigger DRAW ELEMENT:Wood FILLEDCIRCLE 160 160 30 3000

REMOVETRIGGER FirezTrigger
